
= resource person for the conference, [[Re-Thinking Property for a Well-Being Society]]


=Bio=

"Khesang Tshomo has long standing experience in organic sector development. She was Programme Officer, Horticulture Research at the Council of Renewable Natural Resources Research of Bhutan for 10 years. Now she is a Coordinator for the National Organic Programme, Ministry of Agriculture, Bhutan. Khesang works with farmers and extension, coordinating and facilitating multi-sector collaboration in common sector development and promotion of organic farming."


